{"tid":1463570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地應該不停搭車出入機場","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:37:54.000Z","uid":37894,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8170be8c1ff1530c4e2ffbbc9d778da8daa57bd","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"佢地琴日取消航班係因為入機場同離開機場嘅流量爆左，好似我地有data但又上唔到網咁。<br />\n<br />\n今次運動嘅重點係機場交通，大家留喺機場係唔夠，琴日停飛喺主因唔係堵塞，係流量。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地應該不停進出機場，用盡機場交通嘅流量，令入機場嘅人排大隊，想離開嘅人因排隊走而滯留，等多d人被迫留機場或者上唔到機。<br />\n<br />\n我地出入機場合情合法合法，就可以隊爆機場嘅交通流量。唔洗阻人登又唔洗同人衝突。"},{"pid":"a15a42063a8e572bf7ac5e0b4c26858bca1aff56","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"A車又好 E車又好，地鐵都好"},{"pid":"bab91c7841b8d94b2734c9e7165b03f6a0524135","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"搭車唔犯法"},{"pid":"a315a3932bd690bd7f62b79cef58998e12bfda62","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39e8ccd6b3cd7bd377d22fe7e43b1fc8e88bb197","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"606d399d117745c5a0fb26d9df977a0b6458e75a","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42380680754a79c3ea78038d7f627a5fc7ef4eac","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df114c7ff2937410ab5c6a14e3cce6ad84e81961","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42ad8cdb1e926020f3dc11cf3c56d824503f4adb","tid":1463570,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51a80a9f2b8ca29dedf2763ade1